description: Stylish and thoughtfully appointed studio at FP3 — Fort Point’s sought-after boutique building known for its architectural character and creative energy. This comfortable, open-concept home features refined designer details, including grasscloth accent wall, curated lighting, custom window treatments, and wide-plank maple flooring. A sleek, modern kitchen offers contemporary cabinetry, stone countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Oversized windows and high ceilings enhance the sense of space, while in-unit laundry, central air, and a full modern bath add everyday ease. FP3 offers 24/7 concierge, elevator, a common roof deck with gas grill, and a rotating art gallery in the lobby. Located moments from South Station, Trader Joe’s, the ICA, and some of the Seaport’s best dining and cultural destinations.
